data.description: Newly remodeled, Price Reduction Sellers Motivated 2/2.5 townhouse in Heritage Village. Modern convenience meets elegance with a full-size washer & dryer in-unit, while the fenced patio sets the stage for delightful entertaining/relaxing. Embrace a lifestyle of leisure with many community amenities, including scenic club house, tennis, racquetball, basketball, and pickle-ball courts. Let your family thrive playgrounds and invigorating exercise trails. Discover the perfect blend of tranquility and excitement just 1.5 miles away from ''The Ballpark of the Palm Beaches,'' the spring training home to the Washington Nationals and Houston Astros. Experience a harmonious blend of comfort, style, and recreation. Don't miss the opportunity to call this townhouse your home.
